    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Here & Now
---
One day at a time -- this is enough. Do not look back and grieve over the
past, for it is gone; and do not be troubled about the future, for it has
not yet come. Live in the present, and make it so beautiful that it would
be worth remembering.
